All Classes

Class Summary 
Class Description
Animal
Keeps information about impact on plants and range for moving.
AnimalLocation
Keeps pair of Animal and its Coordinates
AnimalLocationTest  
AnimalsPositions
Keeps all Animals with their positions.
Bee
Sets impact and range for Bee
Borer
Sets impact and range for Borer
Coordinates
Keeps information about X and Y coordinate.
DayOfYear
Keeps information about number of the day in simulation and returns current Season of the year.
Flower
Defines how to evaluate impacts of Weather and Animals for flowers
Fruit
Defines how to evaluate impacts of Weather and Animals for fruits
Garden
Keeps information about position of plants and animals.
GardenProperties
Keeps information about size of the garden and what was the starting number of plants and shows what is the maximum number of plants that can be in the garden
GardenProperties.GardenDimensions
Keeps information about width and height of the garden
GardenPropertiesTest  
Main
Main class for starting the simulation and interaction with user.
Mole
Sets impact and range for Mole
Plants
Keeps information about Plant, its life and growth phase status and upgrades them.
PlantsPositions
Keeps all Plants with their positions.
RandomAnimalGenerator
Generates random Animal out of Bee, Borer and Mole
RandomAnimalsPositionGenerator
Generates random position for Animals.
RandomPlantGenerator
Generates random Plant out of Flower, Fruit and Vegetable
RandomPlantsPositionGenerator
Generates random positions for Plants.
Season
Keeps name of the current Season
Simulation
Runs simulation based on GardenProperties and shows logs.
UserInteractor
Interaction with user, asking for size of the garden and staring number of plants
Vegetable
Defines how to evaluate impacts of Weather and Animals for vegetables
WeatherConditions
Keeps status of the weather.
